column1: # Supplementary Dataset S11. This tab delmited table contains the results of the eQTL linkage results of the 6464 sense traits at 5% FDR.
# This tab delmited table is the results of the eQTL linkage results
# of the 6464 sense traits at 5% FDR. Each row correspond
# to one linkage between a expression trait (gene)its eQTL. When
# a trait was linked to more several locus correlated more than 0.8
# we considered that it corresponded to a single QTL, which position
# could not be determined. they were regroup.
# Here each row correpond to a group and the different location
# of the grouped QTL are separated with coma.
# First field is the name of sense trait (target)
# Next 3 fields are the coordinate of the QTL as a
#  genomic interval. Note that each QTL is considered
#  as spanning in between the first non linked variant.
# next field is an indicater of whether the linkage correspong to
#  a cis or a trans linakge.
# Next field indicate the strongest candiate regulator as this locus
#  predicted unsing correlation between the trait and the regulator
#  regulator is a coding or non-coding genes
